title: Lunchbox Guesses Weight + Graffiti In Amy’s Neighborhood + Guitar Riff Game

description:
Lunchbox only gets to ask listeners a few questions and then he has to guess how much they weigh within five pounds. Amy is concerned about covering up graffiti in her neighborhood. Plus, we play the guitar riff game!
